data.description: This adorable 3 bedroom & 2 full bath home sits on a very large lot with an oversized 2 car garage. This open floor plan features beautiful flooring, nice warm cabinetry, granite kitchen countertops, and stainless steel appliances. This home has a primary bedroom with an ensuite. New roof installed in 2019.  The following were updated in 2017: lighting; bathrooms; vanities; tub enclosures; toilets; electric with interconnected smoke detectors and 200 amp panel.  The large oversized garage was constructed in 2017 and has electric inside it.  Schedule your personal tour today!
